types of inhertiance 
_________________________
Type	                Description	                           			  Example
Single Inheritance	One child class inherits from one parent class.      	A → B

Multiple Inheritance  One child class inherits from multiple parent classes.  A, B → C
Multilevel Inheritance  One class inherits from another child class.          A → B → C
Hierarchical Inheritance  Multiple child classes inherit from one parent class.  A → B, C
Hybrid Inheritance       Combination of multiple types of inheritance.            	Complex hierarchy





